overview.en: TTC: Tutorcoin is a smart contract for online education platform. We are building a next generation online education & knowledge share platform. Though our platform, every people can get educated or share his/her knowledge easily and efficiently.
overview.zh: TTC: Tutorcoin 是专注于在线教育和知识分享的智能合约。 我们致力于打造下一代在线教育平台， 帮助人们更有效率的接受教育和共享知识。
